reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and Functional - Perfect for My Bedroom!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the EnHomee 12 Drawer Dresser with Wooden Top, and I am extremely pleased with its quality and design. This dresser has elevated the aesthetics of my bedroom while providing ample storage space for all my belongings.First and foremost, the wooden top of this dresser adds a touch of elegance to my room. The smooth, polished surface beautifully complements the overall design, making it a standout piece of furniture. It feels sturdy and well-crafted, and the natural wood finish adds warmth to the room.The 12 drawers are a great feature of this dresser, offering versatility and practicality. I love how spacious they are, allowing me to easily organize my clothes, accessories, and other personal belongings. The drawers slide smoothly, and their deep design ensures that I can store even bulkier items without any hassle.The build quality of the EnHomee Dresser is remarkable. The frame is made of high-quality materials, which are evident in its solid construction. The drawer handles are also sturdy and well-designed, adding a touch of sophistication to the overall appearance.Assembly was straightforward and hassle-free. The package included clear instructions, and all the necessary hardware was provided. I was able to put it together without any assistance, and it took me approximately an hour to complete.Another great aspect of this dresser is its size. It is neither too bulky nor too small, making it perfect for rooms of various sizes. It does not overpower the space, but rather enhances it with its sleek design.In terms of functionality, I appreciate the thoughtful design of this dresser. The drawers are easy to open and close, and they have a good depth to accommodate a wide range of items. The wooden top is also spacious enough to display some decorative items or utilize it as additional surface space.Overall, the EnHomee 12 Drawer Dresser with Wooden Top has exceeded my expectations. It combines style, functionality, and quality craftsmanship, making it a fantastic addition to any bedroom. I highly recommend this dresser to anyone in need of an attractive and practical storage solution.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These tower drawers are an amazing value for the money. I really like that the drawers/bins easily slide in and out, completely to look through. It offers SO much extra storage it's unbelievable. I ordered two of these and actually have empty drawers for other items. I never had 'places' to put misc. items. Regular dressers don't offer enough space, they are bulky and hard to move around. And cubbies storage or shelves don't work to contain the clutter. Folded stacks can easily fall over etc.. These tower drawers are big enough to hold adult items of clothing (especially undergarments, socks, pajamas, leggings, t-shirts, work out sets, jeans, seasonal clothing, etc). I also store bulk items that I buy, such as shampoo, soap, lotion freeing up my under sink cabinets and linen closets. Also, I have literally cleared my messy bathroom counters by storing in the bins, what I used to leave on the counter top. I bring the bin to where I get ready and easily put away when done (by keeping curlers, blow dryer, cosmetics neatly under wraps). Even if you have to leave it out it's still easier to tuck it away then looking at cleaning up a whole messy counter. YES! I note this as some reviews said it's good enough for kids clothing storage only. Also the height makes 12 drawers/bin storage available, however, the profile is sleek and not too deep. They are easy to slide to clean around and under (not attaching to wall as I have no young kids & I am planning on putting slide pads under them). Also I just use a swifter type duster to dust the top /front/sides/underneath and it works great. I have much more room in my closet for hanging garments since I now store those clothing items in this unit. I couldn't recommend this item more for quick, affordable storage solutions.
